clusterList.phrase: just a heads up that ok is making a showing at the upcoming linuxworld conference in san francisco on tuesday august 5th at 4pm the group is headed to thirstybear brew co to throw a few back if there are any hackers out in northern california that would like to discuss microkernel technology share ideas or just hang out come and grab a drink with us at thirstybear around 4pm onwards for those that don't know the bar is at thirstybear brewing company 661 howard st san francisco california 94105 telephone 415-974-0905 tim and gernot will be in their black ok t-shirts and should be pretty easy to find
